The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | Double victory for Mahesh Bhupathi
                                                                                                                                                                                                     Double victory for Mahesh Bhupathi
                      
	New York: Mahesh Bhupathi and his partner Mark Knowles scored a comfortable straight-set win to advance to the second round of the US Open.         
	Meanwhile, in mixed doubles, Bhupathi and his Australian partner Samantha Stosur defeated Americans Alexa Glatch and Scott Lipsky 6-3, 6-3 to move into round II.         
	Bhupathi and Knowles defeated the Swedish pair of Johan Brunstrom and Thomas Johansson 6-3, 6-4 in a little over one hour on Thursday.         
	The Indo-Bahamian pair did not face even a single break point in the match and broke their Swedish opponents once in each set to move to the next round.         
	Leander Paes has already reached the second round along with his Czech partner Lukas Dlouhy and face Eduardo Schwank of Argentina and Potito Starace of Italy.         
	Bhupathi and Knowles face Swiss Yves Allegro and Romanian Horia Tecau in their second round. (PTI)                                                                                                                          
